{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0dd523d87d","title":"给徐向前“的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ad7e4fd6e7","index":0,"year":1948,"month":11,"day":29,"articleId":"0dd523d87d"}],"tags":[{"id":"0ed2104fe1","name":"徐向前","type":"人物"},{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fcb90f8a15","type":"paragraph","text":"给徐向前“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"0dd523d87d"},{"id":"93980e3a35","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年11月29日）向前同志：闻病极念，务望安心静养，不要挂念工作，前方指挥由周、胡、陈担负。你病情略好能够移动时即来中央休养，待全愈后再上前线。总之，治疗和休养是第一等重要，病好一切好办。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"0dd523d87d"},{"id":"a1174fabd5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛刘朱周任","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"0dd523d87d"},{"id":"f75362009d","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月二十九日[1]徐向前（1901-1990），山西五台人。当时任华北军区副司令员、华北野战军第一兵团司令员兼政治委员。[2]周，指周士第（1900-1979），广东琼海人。当时任华北野战军第一兵团副司令员兼副政治委员。胡，指胡耀邦（1915-1989），湖南岗阳1986），广西蒙山人。当时任华北野战军第一兵团参课长。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"0dd523d87d"}],"page":{"id":"ff4032c52d","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"0dd523d87d","start":296,"end":296}}}},"__N_SSG":true}